// v1.8 C3: the `Ok` variant carries `value: T`, and the slot binds
// `T -> Int`. Passing a `String` to `value` should be caught
// statically — pre-v1.8 the analyzer accepted any value because it
// didn't substitute generics into the variant's field types.
// EXPECTED: ≥ 1 × StaticTypeMismatch on the `r.value` field.
{ Result<Int, String> r: Result.Ok { value: "wrong type" } }
